{"tid":1336187,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[721] 兵法學習-圍魏救趙","createTime":"2019-07-20T22:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T07:53:20.000Z","uid":199727,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"003868d4789b8b956deeab776eb323dd3a079f68","tid":1336187,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T22:05:06.000Z","msg":"圍魏救趙是兵法「三十六計」的第二計。原文注釋為：「共敵不如分敵，敵陽不如敵陰。」此計之意思是：<br />\n<br />\n攻打正面強大集中之敵人，不如設法分散它而後再打；例如利用敵人之精銳正在攻打另一國家，並且兩軍相持不下時，趁機攻佔敵方本土，迫使敵人退兵或分兵；<br />\n<br />\n先打擊氣勢旺盛的之敵人，不如尋找機會先打擊敵人虛弱之地方，消滅敵人。"},{"pid":"46d1eea7a3ba5e9463606bcb2e23b23519f307f5","tid":1336187,"uid":199727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T22:07:40.000Z","msg":"港島區咁亂<br />\n當啲暴徒集中哂喺港島時<br />\n我地呢班普通既香港市民去九龍新界購物就安全得多了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9b6b06be0e14b771a927ffcd640ea8bccbc3a6","tid":1336187,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T22:18:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"04053551e4561c0547b73699c51cfa86a436de6a","tid":1336187,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T22:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e20df16c4b706186f464108f72d9a74b6e77a0","tid":1336187,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"46d1eea7a3ba5e9463606bcb2e23b23519f307f5","tid":1336187,"uid":199727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T22:07:40.000Z","msg":"港島區咁亂<br />\n當啲暴徒集中哂喺港島時<br />\n我地呢班普通既香港市民去九龍新界購物就安全得多了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T22:20:24.000Z","msg":"唔一定九龍 港島仲有咁多地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bc078967782f5ac9f71850e3f9ebdda23af57c","tid":1336187,"uid":199